posting_body: ['Mural Apartments', '4727 42nd Avenue Southwest, Seattle, WA, 98116', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 56', 'OR Text', '56', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team.', 'Use the link below for more details:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 695 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'A stroll from your front door takes you to local eateries, eclectic shops, a playhouse, neighborhood pubs, grocery stores, and a favorite old school European deli that has become a West Seattle landmark.', 'There is no set art design—this is a taste of daily life on the Westside, and here you get to sketch your lifestyle.', 'We are closer than you think: just a 12-minute bus ride from downtown lands you in the Alaska Junction, the heart of West Seattle.', 'Surrounded by views of Elliott Bay, the Olympic Mountains and the striking Seattle skyline, Mural celebrates the art of living—where environmental responsibility, functional design, and creativity all call home.', 'Visit our Seattle apartment community today.', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet friendly!', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'vx1Rm4jdyN']
